---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<section class="contact" id="contact">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="contact-inner">
      <div class="contact-lead">
        <span class="mono">§ Contact</span>
        <p class="pitch"><em>Ik breng structuur, regie en voortgang in complexe IT-programma's</em> waar meerdere partijen en belangen samenkomen.</p>

        <div class="problem-cues">
          <p>Heb je te maken met een IT-traject dat complexer is dan vooraf gedacht?</p>
          <p>Of een programma waarin structuur, overzicht en voortgang ontbreken?</p>
        </div>

        <p class="contact-body">
          Dan kan het helpen om iemand tijdelijk aan te laten sluiten die rust en richting brengt. Ik werk als onafhankelijk interim consultant op het snijvlak van IT, organisatie en uitvoering — met focus op regie, planning en bestuurbaarheid in complexe omgevingen.
        </p>

        <p class="contact-invite">Neem gerust contact op voor een eerste kennismaking. <span class="vrijblijvend">Een eerste gesprek is altijd vrijblijvend.</span></p>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-channels">
        <a href="tel:+31646741921" class="channel">
          <span class="mono">— Telefoon</span>
          <span class="channel-big">06 4674 1921</span>
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:agile@solutionxl.nl" class="channel">
          <span class="mono">— E-mail</span>
          <span class="channel-big">agile@solutionxl.nl</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/weele/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="channel">
          <span class="mono">— LinkedIn</span>
          <span class="channel-big">linkedin.com/in/weele</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-legal">
      <address>
        <b>SolutionXL B.V.</b><br />
        Burgemeester Bickerstraat 43, 1111 CA Diemen<br />
        <span class="mono">KvK 72779705</span>
      </address>
      <span class="mono">© {currentYear} SolutionXL BV · Henk van der Weele</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact {
    padding-block: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 9rem) 2.5rem;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .contact::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -50%;
    left: -20%;
    width: 80%;
    height: 120%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 22%, transparent) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .contact-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .contact-lead { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.4rem; }
  .contact-lead .mono { color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 85%, var(--bg)); }

  .pitch {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.6vw, 2.8rem);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    color: var(--bg);
    max-width: 22ch;
  }
  .pitch em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 85%, var(--bg));
  }

  .problem-cues {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 20%, transparent);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    max-width: 42ch;
  }
  .problem-cues p {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--bg);
  }

  .contact-body {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 78%, transparent);
    max-width: 50ch;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .contact-invite {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--bg);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  .vrijblijvend {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 85%, var(--bg));
    font-style: italic;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .contact-channels {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 25%, transparent);
  }

  .channel {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 20%, transparent);
    transition: padding-left 0.3s;
  }
  .channel:hover { padding-left: 1rem; }
  .channel .mono { color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 85%, var(--bg)); }

  .channel-big {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.4vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    color: var(--bg);
  }
  .channel:hover .channel-big {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 85%, var(--bg));
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .footer-legal {
    margin-top: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 20%, transparent);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .footer-legal address {
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 80%, transparent);
  }
  .footer-legal address b { color: var(--bg); font-weight: 500; }
  .footer-legal .mono { color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 55%, transparent); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .contact-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
